Kwik Auto Glass
Kam, a Sacramento local resident has been in the auto repair business for over 20 years. Managing a local shop in Davis, in 1995 Kam decided to start his own businesses, Kwik Auto Glass. He currently works by appointment and servicing local Businesses such as A1 Body Shop, Cooks Collision of Davis, among others. He works closely with customers to accommodate their needs, and works with insurance companies so his customers wont have to pay completely out of pocket for their vehicles glass repairs.
